<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77a6133d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s450rr–2"><num value="450rr–2">§ 450rr–2.</num><heading> Commendation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Congress of the United States highly commends the members of the joint international expedition which discovered the R.M.S. Titanic.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77a6133e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/513/s4">Pub. L. 99–513, § 4</ref>, <date date="1986-10-21">Oct. 21, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/2083">100 Stat. 2083</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
